OL,3,CFormer Barcelona player Dani Alves
OL,4,Cfound guilty of sexual assault
OL,6,FFootballer Dani Alves has been found
OL,7,Fguilty of sexually assaulting a young
OL,8,Fwoman in a Barcelona nightclub, a
OL,9,FSpanish court ruled on Thursday.
OL,11,FThe three-judge panel sentenced Alves
OL,12,Fto four years and six months. He must
OL,13,Falso pay his victim 150,000 euros
OL,14,F(#128,000) in compensation and their
OL,15,Fcourt costs.
OL,17,FAlves, aged 40, denied any wrongdoing
OL,18,Fduring a trial that took place over
OL,19,Fthree days this month. The decision
OL,20,Fcan be appealed.
