OL,3,CFormer Barcelona player Dani Alves
OL,4,Cfound guilty of sexual assault
OL,6,FThe court found Alves sexually
OL,7,Fassaulted his victim early in the
OL,8,Fmorning of December 31, 2022, when she
OL,9,Fsaid he raped her in a bathroom of an
OL,10,Fupscale Barcelona nightclub.
OL,12,FIt was determined by the court that
OL,13,Falcohol intoxication had no legal
OL,14,Frelevance in regards to the "cognitive
OL,15,Ffaculties of the accused" when defence
OL,16,Flawyers for Alves offered his state of
OL,17,Fdrunkenness at the nightclub in
OL,18,Fmitigation.
