OL,3,CFormer Barcelona player Dani Alves
OL,4,Cfound guilty of sexual assault
OL,6,FProsecutors had sought a nine-year
OL,7,Fprison sentence for Alves while the
OL,8,Flawyers representing his accuser
OL,9,Fwanted 12 years.
OL,11,FHis defence asked for his acquittal,
OL,12,For if found guilty a one-year sentence
OL,13,Fplus 50,000 euros (#43,000)
OL,14,Fcompensation for the victim.
OL,16,FAlves has been in jail since being
OL,17,Fdetained early last year. His requests
OL,18,Ffor bail were denied because the court
OL,19,Fconsidered him a flight risk.
