OL,3,CFormer Barcelona player Dani Alves
OL,4,Cfound guilty of sexual assault
OL,6,FAt the peak of his career, the
OL,7,Ffootballer played for several top
OL,8,Fclubs, including Barcelona, Juventus
OL,9,Fand Paris St Germain.
OL,11,FHe also played for Brazil from 2006 to
OL,12,F2022 and is the nation's third most-
OL,13,Fcapped player of all times.
OL,15,FHis most recent club, Mexican side
OL,16,FPumas UNAM, terminated his contract
OL,17,Fafter the charges were brought against
OL,18,Fhim in January 2023.
